{"data":[{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 21/03/2018 05:37 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/3: Messi l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do h\u00f3a \"si\u00eau nh\u00e2n\" tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946530\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946530\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Messi h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do h\u1ebft n\u00f4n khan, h\u00f3a \"si\u00eau nh\u00e2n\" tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i:</strong> C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian, NHM t\u1eebng lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Lionel Messi c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00f4n khan tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca l\u1eabn \u0110T Argentina. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/3: Messi l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do h\u00f3a &amp;#34;si\u00eau nh\u00e2n&amp;#34; tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-21-3-Messi-lo-li-do-hoa-dfsg-1521579926-664-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Messi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f3i quen dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00ec s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb si\u00eau sao 30 tu\u1ed5i, b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap anh kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 do thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9, th\u00f3i quen \u0103n u\u1ed1ng b\u1eefa b\u00e3i: \u201cTh\u1eddi gian \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 khi t\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u00e0o mi\u1ec7ng: s\u00f4 c\u00f4 la, b\u00e1nh quy, pizza, \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 ga, khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3 b\u1ecf \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao MU t\u1eebng gh\u00e9t cay gh\u00e9t \u0111\u1eafng Sanchez:</strong> Tr\u00ean k\u00eanh TyC Sports (Argentina), h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201cng\u00e3 ng\u1eeda: khi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u201cAlexis l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0ng th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a nhau m\u1ea5y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. M\u1ed7i khi MU \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Arsenal hay Argentina g\u1eb7p Chile, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n cho anh ta \u0103n m\u1ed9t c\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i t\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh khi bi\u1ebft MU c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sanchez, gi\u1edd th\u00ec anh ta \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i\u201d, tr\u00edch l\u1eddi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Real v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng mua \u201cMessi trong khung g\u1ed7\u201d: </strong>Alisson l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a AS Roma c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110T Brazil, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cMessi trong khung g\u1ed7\u201d. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm hai \u201c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u201d Real Madrid v\u00e0 Liverpool.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Roma, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>V\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU tr\u1ecdng th\u01b0\u1edfng, Young \u0111\u00e3 \u201cd\u1ea1y d\u1ed7\u201d \u0111\u00e0n em:</strong> Ashley Young v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tin vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw v\u00e0o \u201cng\u00f5 c\u1ee5t\u201d. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, HLV Jose Mourinho th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng ch\u00ea bai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brighton 2-0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft FA Cup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Young \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0n em: \u201cKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Shaw m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1eadt ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. T\u00f4i tin Shaw s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao Liverpool kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec7 t\u1eed Pep:</strong> Tr\u00ean Daily Mail, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Pep Guardiola li\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y v\u00ec \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00e0i n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m, Jurgen Klopp.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Barcelona: \u201dTam gi\u00e1c qu\u1ef7\u201d d\u1ea7n s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng, ai gi\u00fap Messi - Coutinho?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-16/barce_midfield-640-1521174625-600-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Barcelona: \u201dTam gi\u00e1c qu\u1ef7\u201d d\u1ea7n s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng, ai gi\u00fap Messi - Coutinho?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Barcelona \u0111ang d\u1ea7n chia tay v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao sau 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-21-3-messi-lo-li-do-hoa-sieu-nhan-tro-lai-c409a946530.html","id":"439"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 21/03/2018 03:51 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: N\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n k\u00e9p\u201d Arsenal sau Sanchez","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946529\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946529\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>MU g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: N\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n k\u00e9p\" Arsenal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n MU \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thay th\u1ebf Antonio Valencia trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: N\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n k\u00e9p\u201d Arsenal sau Sanchez - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-No-bom-tan-kep-Arsenal-sau-Sanchez----twtewe-1521577203-190-width660height495.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Bellerin, MU c\u00f2n t\u00ednh \"cu\u1ed7m\" lu\u00f4n Ramsey t\u1eeb Arsenal</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Telegraph, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t v\u1edbi BL\u0110 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea3 Aaron Ramsey (m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ch\u01b0a ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9). M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c&nbsp;c\u1ea1nh tranh&nbsp;su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh (m\u1edbi ra s\u00e2n 23 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ghi 7 b\u00e0n).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham quy\u1ebft tranh Bale</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u1edf TBN v\u00e0 Anh \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0a tin Gareth Bale b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u201cl\u1eadt k\u00e8o\u201d MU sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Tottenham.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay, Daily Star x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ph\u00eda \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n Bale tr\u1edf v\u1ec1. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7, HLV Mauricio Pochettino v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn&nbsp;m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 100 tri\u1ec7u euro (89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham \u201cch\u1ed1t\u201d gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Lukaku</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u201chot\u201d nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh MU, ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Real Madrid, PSG, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m nh\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 trung v\u1ec7 l\u1eabn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2019, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng kho\u1ea3ng 29 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo Daily Star, BL\u0110 Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u00e0o tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 42 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chelsea chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 Luke Shaw</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MU nh\u1eafm Alderweireld, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0 Chelsea, Arsenal, Liverpool, Everton \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng dang tay c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt anh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Mirror cho hay, Chelsea \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1p&nbsp;\u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1eabn l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng (Shaw \u0111ang nh\u1eadn 80 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n \u1edf MU), m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u201cThe Blues\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao Napoli l\u1ea1i \"b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh\"</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jorginho, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean k\u00eanh ph\u00e1t thanh Radio Crc (Italia), Joao Santos \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c gia Italia x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda MU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Lukaku k\u1ebft th\u00e2n Sanchez, phe Mourinho c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh: Pogba s\u1eafp ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-21/640lu1-1521566767-992-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Lukaku k\u1ebft th\u00e2n Sanchez, phe Mourinho c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh: Pogba s\u1eafp ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Paul Pogba \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp tai Old Trafford.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-no-bom-tan-kep-arsenal-sau-sanchez-c409a946529.html","id":"438"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 20/03/2018 05:22 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/3: HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Pogba","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946304\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946304\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Pogba:</strong> \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Colombia v\u00e0 Nga. HLV Deschamps x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: \u201cPogba \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf MU. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho \u0110TQG v\u00e0 World Cup 2018\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/3: HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Pogba - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-20-3-HLV-tuyen-Phap-canh-bao-Pogba-hot-pog-1521497088-535-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4m m\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn World Cup 2018</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shaw s\u1ebd hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU:</strong> Paul Scholes \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Luke Shaw r\u1eddi MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d, Shaw s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1i \u0111a \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ronaldinho l\u1ea5y l\u00f2ng c\u1ea3 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo: </strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 38, Ronaldinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u201cRo v\u1ea9u\u201d nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi mang l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. NHM \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 gi\u1eefa hai thi\u00ean t\u00e0i xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ec9: </strong>HLV Martinez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a HLV Conte t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Th\u1eddi gian qua, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1eaft Hazard \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u201cs\u1ed1 9\u201d th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Hazard kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy&nbsp; t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1 r\u1ed1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kane 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1eaft h\u01a1n Messi:</strong> Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Cies Football Observatory, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Kane hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Messi 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1edfi Kane \u00edt h\u01a1n Leo 6 tu\u1ed5i. Tottenham c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm b\u1ed9n ti\u1ec1n n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Dele Alli, b\u1edfi c\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean, sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 139 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1eaft th\u1ee9 3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/1521483490-968-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>MU \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-20-3-hlv-tuyen-phap-canh-bao-pogba-c409a946304.html","id":"437"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 20/03/2018 03:17 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946298\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946298\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, MU quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Arsenal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Daily Mirror cho bi\u1ebft, hi\u1ec7n <strong>MU </strong>\u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Arsenal y\u00eau c\u1ea7u trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Hector Bellerin v\u00e0o h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u0103m le mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Bao-chi-50-trieu-bang-quyet-mua-sao-Arsenal-noticia-hector-belerin-1521483544-42-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Bellerin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 MU v\u00e0 Juve quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Bellerin v\u1edbi Arsenal c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn n\u0103m 2023. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf l\u00f2 La Masia c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger v\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 mua 4-5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ra gi\u00e1 \u201cc\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng\u201d mua tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>MU</em> \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00f2n Ashley Young \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao tu\u1ed5i. C\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Marcos Alonso v\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Don Balon (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Man \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ebfn 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngay h\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao khi Alonso v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u201cThe Blues\u201d su\u1ed1t 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho ru\u1ed3ng r\u1eaby Luke Shaw, Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea tranh nhau xin \u201cgi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u\u201d</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd Daily Star cho hay, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi Luke Shaw v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thanh l\u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i m\u00e0 <u>MU</u> t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua anh v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Southampton h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh London l\u00e0 Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng dang tay ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Young \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tin uy t\u00edn t\u1eeb MEN Sport cho bi\u1ebft, nh\u1eb1m t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Ashley Young m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, BL\u0110 MU \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eeba cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eeba k\u00fd k\u1ebft th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cPh\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d mua \u201csao mai\u201d 17 tu\u1ed5i</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed trinh s\u00e1t theo d\u00f5i g\u1eaft gao Ryan Sessegnon v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw s\u1eafp ra \u0111i. Hi\u1ec7n ngo\u00e0i \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d, Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u0103m le mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Craven Cottage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-20/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Bao-chi-50-trieu-bang-quyet-mua-sao-Arsenal-9282042301-1521483544-594-width660height439.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: B\u1ea1o chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft mua sao Arsenal - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ryan Sessegnon (Fulham) l\u00e0 \"sao mai\" \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i \u0111\u1ee5ng Tottenham FA Cup: Mourinho b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u00fd tr\u1eddi?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-19/1521427412-670-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i \u0111\u1ee5ng Tottenham FA Cup: Mourinho b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u00fd tr\u1eddi?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho d\u00e2ng cao trong C\u0110V MU, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ebd t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-bao-chi-50-trieu-bang-quyet-mua-sao-arsenal-c409a946298.html","id":"436"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 19/03/2018 00:15 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/3: Ti\u00ean tri d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o Neymar l\u1ee1 World Cup","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-946001\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-946001\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Ti\u00ean tri d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o Neymar l\u1ee1 World Cup:</strong> H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, trong m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1edf Nam M\u1ef9, nh\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri Carlinhos Vidente \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Neymar s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 5-7 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 3) d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/3: Ti\u00ean tri d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o Neymar l\u1ee1 World Cup - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-18/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-19-3-Tien-tri-du-bao-Neymar-lo-World-Cup-neymar-1521380571-92-width660height445.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Neymar trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn PSG th\u1eafng Marseille h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. C\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 n\u00f3i \u201cTi\u1ec3u Pele\u201d s\u1ebd r\u1eddi xa s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong v\u00f2ng 2-3 th\u00e1ng, ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng n\u1eeda th\u1eddi gian m\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri Carlinhos n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Real Madrid t\u00ecm \u201cti\u1ec3u Modric\u201d: </strong>T\u1edd Marca \u0111\u01b0a tin, Real Madrid b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Luka Modric. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, do v\u1eady, \u201cLos Blancos\u201d s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c s\u0103n ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Salah tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Man City: </strong>Sau l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, l\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Liverpool ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man City \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. Man xanh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng Salah kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u201cThe Kop\u201d kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1n d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t k\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ai v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bayern t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed5i James l\u1ea5y Dembele:</strong> Theo Don Balon, Bayern Munich \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi James Rodriguez r\u1ed3i sau n\u00e0y d\u00f9ng anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng quay v\u1ec1 Real Madrid n\u1ebfu Zinedine Zidane r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi CLB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca ch\u1ea5m Isco thay Iniesta: </strong>Andres Iniesta, 34 tu\u1ed5i, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 cho Barca hay ra \u0111i. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, hay \u0111\u1ea1i gia Trung Qu\u1ed1c ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ini. Barca mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng. Isco c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cBlaugrana\u201d th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Terry v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u:</strong> Trung v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u John Terry,&nbsp;37 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa cho Aston Villa. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1eabn tinh th\u1ea7n cho tham v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Neymar ch\u00e1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, Real s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n: \u201cB\u1ed1 gi\u00e0\u201d khi\u1ebfn PSG ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-17/psg1-1521299008-171-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Neymar ch\u00e1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, Real s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n: \u201cB\u1ed1 gi\u00e0\u201d khi\u1ebfn PSG ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Neymar \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y qu\u00e1 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Ligue I.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-19-3-tien-tri-du-bao-neymar-lo-world-cup-c409a946001.html","id":"435"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 18/03/2018 05:04 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/3: Zidane t\u1ef1 tin k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Neymar","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-945872\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-945872\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Zidane t\u1ef1 tin k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Neymar v\u00e0 Ronaldo: </strong>Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \"ti\u1ec3u Pele\" s\u1ebd h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c si\u00eau sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Real nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, Bale, Benzema n\u1ebfu BL\u0110 \"\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia\" mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/3: Zidane t\u1ef1 tin k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Neymar - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-18/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-18-3-Zidane-tu-tin-ket-hop-Ronaldo---Neymar-dsafsdfsd-1521314131-42-width660height411.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Zidane t\u1ef1 tin Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \"h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p\" v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i cho Real. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y&nbsp;s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n hay kh\u00f4ng \u00e0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a CLB&nbsp;c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba, Sanchez\": </strong>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Alan Shearer sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00fang t\u00fang trong vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa&nbsp;Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"MU chi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba nh\u01b0ng Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch khai th\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Pogba th\u1eadm ch\u00ed&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Sanchez c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m t\u01b0\u1edfng MU ch\u1ec9 mua v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u sa s\u00fat d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Mourinho\", tr\u00edch l\u1eddi c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 47 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"Real, Barca l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 v\u00ec s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo, Messi\":</strong> \u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League, HLV Carlo Ancelotti kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i \"\u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda\" cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barca. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia,&nbsp;hai g\u00e3 kh\u1ed3ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t: Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Ancelotti c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao hai CLB qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, Juventus v\u00e0 AS Roma - nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Real, Barca \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft: \"Real v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec kinh nghi\u1ec7m, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf Champions League c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo, Messi.&nbsp;Juventus v\u00e0 Roma kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \